"Igama lakho lomsebenzisi nephasiwedi akufani. Sicela uzame futhi.
(Ukuthola futhi ukwaziswa kwe-akhawunti, iya ku http://google.com/ama-akhawunti.)"
Ngezizathu zokuphepha sicela ufake igama eliboniswe ngenhla

"Siyakuhalalisela! I-Android yakho manje isihlanganiswe ne-Akhawunti ye-Google
%s."
Sekela ngokulondoloza idatha ne-Akhawunti yami ye-Google

I-Google yakho nezinye izilungiselelo zezinhlelo zokusebenza zelungu langaphandle nenye idatha (njengamabhukimakhi namaphasiwedi e-Wi-Fi) angasekelwa ngokulondoloza kwiziphakeli ze-Google, nge-Akhawunti yakho ye-Google.
